quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  103,1,Ndayira omulembe (buli mulembe)
  103,2,Mazima ddala omuntu yenna gy’afa yenkana ali mu kufaafaaganirwa
  103,3,"Okugyako abo abakkiriza Katonda (mu nzikiriza entuufu) ate ne bakola e mirimu emirungi, era ne balaamirigana okukoleranga ku mazima (mu bulamu bwabwe bwonna) era ne balaamiragana okubeera abagumikiriza (mu bulamu bwabwe bwonna)"